                ">>Calcul de $b$ :",
                "$$b = \\lim_{x \\to +\\infty} [f(x) - 2x] = \\lim_{x \\to +\\infty} \\left[\\dfrac{2x^2 + x - 1}{x - 1} - 2x\\right]$$",
                "$$= \\lim_{x \\to +\\infty} \\dfrac{2x^2 + x - 1 - 2x(x - 1)}{x - 1} = \\lim_{x \\to +\\infty} \\dfrac{2x^2 + x - 1 - 2x^2 + 2x}{x - 1}$$",
                "$$= \\lim_{x \\to +\\infty} \\dfrac{3x - 1}{x - 1} = \\lim_{x \\to +\\infty} \\dfrac{3 - \\frac{1}{x}}{1 - \\frac{1}{x}} = ___3___$$",
