                "$$f'(x) = 3x^2 - 6x + 2$$",
                "$$f''(x) = 6x - 6 = 6(x - ___1___)$$",
                ">>Tableau de signes de $f''(x)$ :",
                "$$\\begin{array}{c|ccc} x & -\\infty & & 1 & & +\\infty \\\\ \\hline f''(x) & & - & 0 & + & \\\\ \\hline \\mathcal{C}_f & & \\text{concave} & & \\text{convexe} & \\end{array}$$",
                ">>Conclusion :",
